Version 0.1 (2010-01-27)
 - Initial version
   - Basic operation supports:
     - Allocate and delete job template
     - Run single job
     - Wait for a job
     - Set remote command
     - Set command arguments
     - Set command environment
     - Set join_files flag
   - Basic usage examples exist
     - run_job.erl
     - wait_job.erl
